        <num>CC 3167</num>
        <heading>3167.  Pledgee not bound for pledgor's obligations</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3167.  Pledgee not bound for pledgor's obligations
In the absence of an assumption by the pledgee, the existence of a pledge does not
impose upon the pledgee liability for the pledgor's acts or omissions, nor does it bind the
pledgee to perform the pledgor's obligations.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
